        "id": 6250
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-07-10T18:05:15Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Is there a reason we have to do the detach here?\n\nIf we moved it down to mapStagingBuffers(), we could call mapWriteAsync() and add it to the busy list in one step. Then we wouldn\u0027t need to rely on the ordering of buffers in the busy list to know which ones to map.\n\nWould that break something?",
      "revId": "f6d4a4eeb224d78f23a90d479472e7b31dc86683",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
